            <fr:title text="Irreducible affine schemes have integral global section">Irreducible affine schemes have integral global section</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Lemma</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter><html:p>
  For an <fr:link href="/schm-IFX1/" title="Affine scheme" uri="https://charloced.github.io/schm-IFX1/" display-uri="schm-IFX1" type="local">affine scheme</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\operatorname {Spec} A]]></fr:tex>, it is <fr:link href="/schm-HKT4/" title="Irreducible schemes" uri="https://charloced.github.io/schm-HKT4/" display-uri="schm-HKT4" type="local">irreducible</fr:link> iff <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="/idem-comm-487K/" title="Integral distributive lattices" uri="https://charloced.github.io/idem-comm-487K/" display-uri="idem-comm-487K" type="local">integral</fr:link>.
</html:p>
 
   
   <fr:tree show-metadata="false" toc="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:authors /><fr:date><fr:year>2025</fr:year><fr:month>6</fr:month><fr:day>10</fr:day></fr:date><fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
  Since <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\operatorname {Spec} D]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="/topl-FII1/" title="Sober spaces" uri="https://charloced.github.io/topl-FII1/" display-uri="topl-FII1" type="local">sober</fr:link> by <fr:link href="/idem-comm-EA6S/" title="Spectra are spectral spaces" uri="https://charloced.github.io/idem-comm-EA6S/" display-uri="idem-comm-EA6S" type="local">Theorem <fr:contextual-number uri="https://charloced.github.io/idem-comm-EA6S/" display-uri="idem-comm-EA6S" /></fr:link>, it is irreducible iff it has a generic point, i.e. iff <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[D]]></fr:tex> has a unique maximal filter. This holds iff <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[D]]></fr:tex> is integral by the dual statement of <fr:link href="/idem-comm-EV8L/" title="Quotient of prime filters are local" uri="https://charloced.github.io/idem-comm-EV8L/" display-uri="idem-comm-EV8L" type="local">Proposition <fr:contextual-number uri="https://charloced.github.io/idem-comm-EV8L/" display-uri="idem-comm-EV8L" /></fr:link>.
</fr:mainmatter></fr:tree>
 
